column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Something goes bump in Greatest Endsvale, and it has Mopingway concerned.
Oh dear... Oh my, oh dear, this is terrible!
Thank goodness you're here! There's a strange sound coming from the waterway. I think there might be something wrong with the water regulation system.

What if the water starts to flow backwards? Or worse! Everything must be inspected from top to bottom, but time is of the essence, and I can't possibly hope to do it all on my own... Not as quickly as I'd like, at any rate. Please say you will help.
Oh, thank goodness. Look for the water towers to the north and you'll find the regulators.
If you can take care of that, I will see to the rest. We can reconvene here when you've finished.
Inspect the water towers to the north and I will see to the rest.
You hear nothing out of the ordinary.
You hear an odd bubbling murmur. This machine seems to be malfunctioning.
How did everything look on your side?
A murmur by the northeast regulator? Hmmm... I think I know what the problem is.
We released fish into the river so that our guests could go fishing, but they're likely attracted to the heat of the regulators.
Not to worry! This is but one little bump on the road to building a fantastic recreational facility, and thanks to you, the path forward can be made smoother.
When our work is finished, I hope you'll visit again and make the most of what we have to offer.
